Confluent Health Logo
We are a family of physical therapy and occupational therapy companies transforming healthcare by strengthening private practices, developing and educating highly effective clinicians, and lowering healthcare costs through workplace wellness and injury prevention. We are run by physical therapists and provide shared services, continuing education, professional development, mentorships, and true partnerships. Our partners get all the advantages of a large company so they can focus on running their clinical practices and serve their local communities.
